summary: This is an automated email notification from the DOJ's E2 Solutions travel system indicating that a final travel voucher (ID 10810414(1)) is pending review. The voucher is for travel related to the case 'R2 S. v. Epstein - Witness Interview' to California from November 13-15, 2019.

events.title: Witness Interview Travel Commences
events.description: Travel begins for a witness interview related to the R2 S. v. Epstein case.

events.title: Witness Interview Travel Concludes
events.description: Travel concludes for a witness interview related to the R2 S. v. Epstein case.

keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher notification from the DOJ's E2 Solutions system.
The travel was for the purpose of a witness interview in the case 'R2 S. v. Epstein'.
The travel occurred from November 13 to November 15, 2019, to California.
The total voucher expenses were $1,516.64 against an estimated trip cost of $1,583.95.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case in late 2019.
